title: Will Xi Jinping and President Obama discuss cybersecurity? - Video - Technology
text:
Will Xi Jinping and President Obama discuss cybersecurity? China's President Xi Jinping travels to Washington DC to meet President Obama on Thursday amid heightening tensions. Both China and the US accuse each other of rampant hacking. But there are some hopeful signs China and the US may be ready to enter a period of detente - at least on critical infrastructure.
